textDelta: Don't stand and watch me, join in because progress is more fun when others get involved.
If you have a partner during your progress, you may have more fun dancing your way to success.
Progress can be a slow, solo journey like dancing with yourself, but it's still progress.
Dance like no one is watching, so progress like it only matters to you.
